<h1 id="organize-your-lesson-overview" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="organizelesson#organize-your-lesson-overview">¶</a> <big>Organize Your Lesson: Overview</big></h1>
<p><big>Rearranging lesson layout empowers you to maximize the flow of your content. You can make changes at any time. There are two main types of change: reordering the layout of overall lesson content, and changing the size of of individual content in your lesson.</big></p><big>
<h1 id="h-1-individual-anvill-content-elements" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="organizelesson#h-1-individual-anvill-content-elements">¶</a> 1. Individual ANVILL Content Elements</h1>
<h2 id="h-11-resize-content" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="organizelesson#h-11-resize-content">¶</a> 1.1 Resize Content</h2>
<p><img src="../column_2.png" alt="column_2.png" height="300" class="align-right">Lesson content can have a wide landscape layout or shrink to half the size for a  column like appearance.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>As the image on the right shows, reduced size makes it possible to place two pieces of content side-by-side.<br>
 </p>
<p><big>To Change Content Layout:</big></p>
<p><img src="../screen_shot_2020-05-20_at_4.39.10_pm.png" alt="screen_shot_2020-05-20_at_4.39.10_pm.png" height="481" class="align-right"></p>
<ol>
<li>Click on the green pencil icon above the content you want to change.<br>
 </li>
<li>In the menu that opens, select:</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>&quot;Shrink&quot; if you are making landscape column smaller.<br>
 </li>
<li>&quot;Enlarge&quot; if you are reverting smaller content to landscape.<br>
 <br>
Menu Example:<br>
<img src="../enlarge_2.png" alt="enlarge_2.png" height="175"></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="h-12-hide-content-on-lesson" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="organizelesson#h-12-hide-content-on-lesson">¶</a> 1.2 Hide Content on Lesson</h2>
<ol>
<li>Click on the green pencil icon above the content you want to change.</li>
<li>In the menu that opens, click on &quot;Hide.&quot; Once you do, that content will no longer visible on your lesson.</li>
</ol>
<h1 id="h-2-reorder-lesson-layout" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="organizelesson#h-2-reorder-lesson-layout">¶</a> 2. Reorder Lesson Layout</h1>
<p><img src="../vertical_ellipses_in_context.png" alt="vertical_ellipses_in_context.png"></p>
</big><ol><big>
<li>In the bottom right of your Lesson, click on the circle icon with vertical ellipses:  	<br>
<img src="../vertical_ellipses_circe_icon.png" alt="vertical_ellipses_circe_icon.png" height="35" class="align-"></li>
<li>Select &quot;Order&quot; from the menu.</li>
<li>A window representing all of your lesson content will open.</li>
<li>To move content elements, just click on an element then drag it to your desired location in the layout.</li>
</big><li><big>When done, click on the check mark on the top right to exit.</big></li>
</ol>
</big></div></template><template slot="comments"><div><comments></comments></div></template></page></div></body></html>
